  			<div class="block h-full w-full bg-mhamaroon text-white text-center" style="background:#ae1165;">
          <img class="slide-img" src="https://www.mha.org.uk/files/9516/1610/4187/communities.jpg" alt="" style="width:100%;">
          <div class="slide-tx-p">
            <h3 class="text-2xl mb-3 font-bold">MHA Communities</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-10">A gift in your Will could deliver the day-to-day services that help people in later life live their own home for as long as possible and stay truly connected to their community. They enable us to provide exciting and fulfilling social and digital activities, including exercise and cooking classes, practical support such as assistance with shopping or gardening, as well as friendship and companionship.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
