          <img class="slide-img" src="https://www.mha.org.uk/files/5816/1610/4193/life-enhancing.jpg" alt="" style="width:100%;">
          <div class="slide-tx-p">
            <h3 class="text-2xl mb-3 font-bold">Life-enhancing facilities in our care homes</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-10">They pay for the things that enhance the quality of life of our residents, such as a summer house, dementia activity table or exercise equipment, to name a just few.</p>
            <p class="text-xl mb-10">Helping people to continue to live the life they would have hoped for. A life that is enjoyable and connected to others.</p>
          </div>
