          <div class="slide-tx-p">
            <h3 class="text-2xl mb-3 font-bold">Spiritual care</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-10">We place great importance on nurturing the mind, body and spirit of those we care for, and their families, of all faiths and none. A gift in your Will means our chaplains are there for them, providing one-to-one support, a sense of comfort and a listening ear to everyone who needs it.</p>
