  			<div class="block h-full w-full bg-mhamaroon text-white text-center" style="background:#ae1165;">
          <img class="slide-img" src="https://www.mha.org.uk/files/6716/1610/4199/music-therapy.jpg" alt="" style="width:100%;">
          <div class="slide-tx-p">
            <h3 class="text-2xl mb-3 font-bold">Music therapy</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-10">Your gift can make connections that matter through the ever-lasting power of music. Our award-winning music therapy service helps people living with dementia in a way that very little else can.</p>
            <p class="text-lg mb-10">Bringing peace and meaning to those living with dementia through stimulating cognition. Helping to reduce symptoms associated with dementia including anxiety and agitation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
