  		<label for="carousel-1" class="next control-4 mha-nav-btn w-10 h-10 mr-2 md:mr-10 absolute cursor-pointer hidden text-3xl font-bold text-white rounded-full bg-mhamaroon hover:bg-mhateal leading-tight text-center z-10 inset-y-0 right-0 my-auto">›</label>

